There really are no words to express how heartbroken we are. Watching the ongoing bushfire crisis unfold here in Australia has been simply devastating. We’ve been giving considered thought to how we can help in the best way possible – more about this in the coming days.⁠
⁠
In the meantime, please help however you can. If you’re in a position to donate – no matter how big or small – check out the organisations below (there are many more, so please feel free to add them in the comments). If you’re not in a financial position to donate, please help spread the word so others will.⁠
⁠
