#bushfires #australianbushfires #crisis #donate #australia #climatechange⁠

Our hearts are broken for all those affected by Australia's devastating bushfires. It's hard for many of us to even comprehend losing everything and having to start over. This is why we hope our simple gesture of donating underwear and socks to those who have lost their homes will help even in the smallest way. ⁠
⁠
We're donating our comfy undies and socks made from organically-grown bamboo to @thread_together who will distribute the garments directly to a relief centre.⁠
⁠
If you would like to make a donation to those affected by the fires or the brave people fighting them, please check out the organisations below (there are many more, please feel free to add them in the comments below):⁠
⁠
